{"tid":1523493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇太子手足走唔到，入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T15:56:42.000Z","uid":83257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"63039edf155e38fdf8e65019068806fd16e70155","tid":1523493,"uid":83257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"有既，留個tg"},{"pid":"d77d1e58f41fc78c8ad18399b004ac25797d6d41","tid":1523493,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站  拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n吹大雞每個站都黎個大清洗<br />\n等狗鐵永久不能運作 齊齊唔洗返工 仲正過塞機場<br />\n唔通爆黑社會麻雀館 就係極限? 黑社會定係狗鐵(政府)仆街D?<br />\n塞鐵已經無用 要直接令全港狗鐵收皮<br />\n今晚咁既下場 就係狗鐵害既 其實都唔止今晚<br />\n你估落去屌D職員有用? 咪撚玩喇<br />\n跳閘? 加價都賺返有突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n站內鋪頭日日唔敢開 <br />\n列車運作唔到 無人坐 齊齊唔洗返工 一係排到仆街去坐巴士<br />\n無人敢再落廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站  拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"187cb42b7dad3e65ec15d9ef238dc7c750d6c905","tid":1523493,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"走唔到點入黎呀..."},{"pid":"7e0049afed59328f8b31466db377b46b4dfb288a","tid":1523493,"uid":83257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"187cb42b7dad3e65ec15d9ef238dc7c750d6c905","tid":1523493,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"走唔到點入黎呀..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"我意思冇車搭走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19aa79fa2dc51b9cc5beb816d5208f3d0193ac00","tid":1523493,"uid":264455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"同問，雖然我係p牌但<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TKr3s1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTKr3s1R.jpg&h=7b93f29